column3: 12 Strong tells the story of the first Special Forces team deployed to Afghanistan after 9/11.
A giant but gentle bull must find a way to break free from his captors and return home to his family.
The story of crime boss John Gotti and his son.
Having taken her first steps into the Jedi world Rey joins Luke Skywalker on an adventure.
Following their win at the world championship the now separated Bellas reunite for one last singing competition at an overseas USO tour.
